:new(title)\r\n\t.id(egui::Id::new(\"demo_window_options\"))\r\n\t.frame(frame) // <-- new\r\n\t.resizable(resizable)\r\n\t.constrain(constrain)\r\n\t.collapsible(collapsible)\r\n\t.title_bar(title_bar)\r\n\t.scroll2(scroll2)\r\n\t.enabled(enabled);\r\n```\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior**\r\nThe title bar should respect margin/stroke settings and have the same width as the rest of the window.","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/emilk/egui/issues/4024/reactions","total_count":1,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":1},"timeline_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/emilk/egui/issues/4024/timeline","performed_via_github_app":null,"state_reason":"completed"}},"event":"cross-referenced"},{"id":15019609464,"node_id":"REFE_lADOCd2s285-mv5NzwAAAAN_PQ14","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/emilk/egui/issues/events/15019609464","actor":{"login":"hacknus","id":33124824,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMzMTI0ODI0","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/33124824?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/hacknus","html_url":"https://github.com/hacknus","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hacknus/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hacknus/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hacknus/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hacknus/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hacknus/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hacknus/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hacknus/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hacknus/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/hacknus/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"event":"referenced","commit_id":"82df725a8cd3bb79f51d885c7e8d49299bce418e","commit_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/hacknus/egui/commits/82df725a8cd3bb79f51d885c7e8d49299bce418e","created_at"